[![version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/yaml2bib)](https://pypi.org/project/yaml2bib/)
[![PyPI - Python Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/yaml2bib)](https://pypi.org/project/yaml2bib/)

### Install
```bash
pip install yaml2bib
```

